snippet.title: Katie - First Look
snippet.description:
"What are you running from?"

Katie is a game about friendship and individuality in a town that simply doesn't care.

Currently produced solely by one man and made with a lot of love during a time of heavy change.

Hopefully coming April 2018 with extra updates to come.
